  <h1>ThinkPad OS</h1>
  <!-- TODO: text-align: right; the button below -->
  <button onclick="document.documentElement.classList.toggle('dark')">Toggle Dark/Light</button>
  <p>Sturdy. Basic. Use forever.</p>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Black magnesium chassis aesthetic <code>Code here</code> more text</li>
      <li>Red TrackPoint® navigation <code>$bash /! y is q great:</code> more text</li>
      <li>Zero rounded corners</li>
      <li>Monospace by default</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <pre>thinkpad ~ % uname -a
  Linux thinkpad-t480 6.8.0-arch1-1 #1 SMP PREEMPT_DYNAMIC Wed, 03 Apr 2024 02:11:22 +0000 x86_64 GNU/Linux

  thinkpad ~ % neofetch --off
        ▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄
