  thinkpad ~ % cat /proc/cpuinfo | grep "model name" | head -1
  model name	: Intel(R) Core(TM) i5-8250U CPU @ 1.60GHz
  </pre>

  <p>To check battery status on a classic ThinkPad, run:</p>

  <code>upower -i /org/freedesktop/UPower/devices/battery_BAT0</code>

  <pre><code>  native-path:          BAT0
    model:                45N1113
    serial:               1234
    vendor:               LGC
    power supply:         yes
    updated:              Sun 07 Feb 2026 14:22:09 (5 seconds ago)
    has history:          yes
    has statistics:       yes
    battery
      present:             yes
      rechargeable:        yes
      state:               discharging
      warning-level:       none
      energy:              23.14 Wh
      energy-empty:        0 Wh
      energy-full:         48.72 Wh
      energy-full-design:  52.5 Wh
      energy-rate:         8.421 W
      time to empty:       2.7 hours
      percentage:          47%
  </code></pre>

  <p>Use the <code>git pull --rebase</code> command when working alone.</p>

  <pre><code>user@thinkpad:~ $ git status
  On branch main
  Your branch is up to date with 'origin/main'.

  nothing to commit, working tree clean
  </code></pre>

  <pre><code># /etc/thinkpad.conf example
  [trackpoint]
  sensitivity = 180
  speed = 120
  </code></pre>

  <button>Click Me</button>
  <a href="#" class="button btn-red">Red Button Action</a>

  <br>
  <br>

  <ul>
    <div>
      Here is some text.
    </div>
    <li>Re-enable middle-click scroll:
      <code>echo -n 1 | sudo tee /sys/devices/platform/i8042/serio1/serio2/drvctl</code></li>
    <li>Check fan speed:
      <code>sudo thinkfan -n</code></li>
    <li>Brightness (0–852 range on many older models):
      <code>echo 600 | sudo tee /sys/class/backlight/intel_backlight/brightness</code></li>
  </ul>

  <ol>
    <li>Coffee</li>
    <li>Tea</li>
    <li>Milk</li>
  </ol>

