  <ol>
    <li>Power on</li>
    <li>Wait for POST beep</li>
    <li>Type really fast</li>
    <li>Reboot if it crashes (it won't)</li>
  </ol>

  <ul>
    <li>Outer item
      <ul>
        <li>Nested level 1</li>
          <ul>
            <li>Nested again</li>
              <ul>
                <li>Nested again</li>
                <li>Here is another</li>
              </ul>
            <li>Here is another</li>
          </ul>
        <li>Another nested</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Back to outer</li>
  </ul>

  <footer>
    Designed to survive 10+ years of reboots • 2026
